- cs.LG (Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new architecture for joint optimization of acoustic and language models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with machine learning models for speech recognition. 
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is also a possible category as the paper deals with processing of speech signals.
